author: Gamers Nexus
description:
Sponsor: Thermalright Frozen Prism 360 on Amazon - https://geni.us/FUqbQC
Hyte is working on a new "X50" series of computer cases with strange, bubbly panel designs, vibrant colors, and an extremely high focus on airflow. Hyte wants to make this case one of the highest performing cases on the market, especially for the price, and will be launching it in the next few months. In this video, we'll talk about the X50 gaming PC case, but we'll also be joined by Rob Teller of Hyte to talk about manufacturing challenges and engineering.

The best way to support our work is through our store: https://store.gamersnexus.net/

Like our content? Please consider becoming our Patron to support us: http://www.patreon.com/gamersnexus
